items.name: Zegna-style suits
items.description:
中国大陆用户可访问 https://www.liblibai.com/#/modal/134 获取该模型

本Lora模型根据杰尼亚西服图片训练，为缺乏服装特征的Stable Diffusion补充图文信息。搭配其他人物模型，可以让人物穿上杰尼亚风格的西服。希望该模型能够抛砖引玉，大家一起来丰富服装设计类目的内容。

模型为测试版本，未来还将添加更多服装风格数据进行训练。目前512*512的压损会模糊服装材质和纹理特征，可能需要更大尺寸的底模才能清晰反映材质和纹理特征。

训练底模：v1-5-pruned-emaonly.ckpt

Prompt参考：zegna, Q22622-221225, Drop+7, Double vents, Notch lapels, Pinpoint pattern, 2-button closure, Flap pockets, Tailored construction, Fully lined, 100%+wool, Charcoal, suits

This Lora model is trained based on Zegna suit images and provides textual information for Stable Diffusion which lacks clothing features. When combined with other character models, it enables characters to wear Zegna-style suits. It is hoped that this model will inspire everyone to enrich the content of the clothing design category.

This model is a test version, and more clothing style data will be added for training in the future. Currently, the 512*512 compression may blur the material and texture features of the clothing, so a larger base model may be needed to clearly reflect these features.

Training base model: v1-5-pruned-emaonly.ckpt

Prompt reference: Zegna, Q22622-221225, Drop+7, Double vents, Notch lapels, Pinpoint pattern, 2-button closure, Flap pockets, Tailored construction, Fully lined, 100%+wool, Charcoal, suits.

items.name: Artek-style furniture
items.description:
中国大陆用户可访问 https://www.liblibai.com/#/modal/136 获取该模型

本Lora模型根据Artek家居产品图片训练，为Stable Diffusion补充北欧风格家居特征。Artek是芬兰著名建筑大师、室内设计师Alvar Aalto(阿尔瓦·阿尔托)和他的妻子Aino Aalto及两位好友Maire Gullichsen和Nils-Gustavhahl共同创立了北欧设计品牌。希望该模型能够抛砖引玉，大家一起来丰富家居产品设计的内容。

模型为测试版本，目前512*512的压损会模糊材质和纹理特征，可能需要更大尺寸的底模才能清晰反映材质和纹理特征。

训练底模：v1-5-pruned-emaonly.ckpt

Prompt参考：artek, Solid birch, Solid birch, Birch plywood, Birch veneer, High-pressure laminate, Linoleum, Fabric upholstery and PU foam padding, Leather upholstery and PU foam padding, Leather upholstery,a small wooden stool with a curved wooden seat on a white background

This Lora model is trained based on Artek home product images, and adds Nordic-style home features to Stable Diffusion. Artek is a famous Nordic design brand founded by Finnish architect and interior designer Alvar Aalto, his wife Aino Aalto, and their two friends Maire Gullichsen and Nils-Gustavhahl. I hope this model can inspire more creative ideas for home product design.

The model is currently in the testing phase, and the 512*512 compression may blur the texture and material features, so a larger base model may be needed to reflect these features more clearly.

Training base model: v1-5-pruned-emaonly.ckpt

Prompt reference: Artek, solid birch, birch plywood, birch veneer, high-pressure laminate, linoleum, fabric upholstery and PU foam padding, leather upholstery and PU foam padding, leather upholstery, a small wooden stool with a curved wooden seat on a white background.

items.name: KenCanMix
items.description:
KenCanMix

This merged model is between 2.8D to realistic.

VAE is required: https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse-original

Hires upscale + Dynamic Thresholding is Highly Recommended.

Recommended Parameters*:

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras, DPM++ 2M Karras

Steps: 25-50

Hires upscaler: Latent (bicubic antialiased), ESRGAN_4x, R-ESRGAN 4x+

Hires upscale: 1.5+

Hires steps: 15+

Denoising strength: 0.4-0.6

CFG scale: 7-10

or

CFG scale: 20-30 + Dynamic Thresholding

Mimic scale: 7-10

Threshold percentile: 99+

Mimic mode: Half Cosine Up

Mimic scale minimum: 3-7

CFG mode: Half Cosine Up

CFG scale minimum: 4-7

Clip skip: 2

*This is just how I use so far, feel free to play around and share with us any better one.

===v.1.0===

If you want Asian faces, LoRA is MUST, and the weight should be higher, try using [from:to:when] prompts. Or applying embeddings such as Ulzzang-6500

Credit to the authors of the following:

Fantasticmix_Real

Lofi

Lyriel

Chikmix

- more realistic on skin, wrinkle, breast shape, skin spots, etc. If you do not like it, negative prompts should work.

items.name: Minustype_UrbanDesign
items.description:
城市相关的全要素模型，在大量的高分辨率效果图上进行分类训练，同时由多个模型融合而成，有较强的泛化能力，适用于大多数与建筑、城市设计相关的生成场景。对于特殊的场景搭配专用的lora和提示词表现会更好。

使用建议：

  1. 建议生成尺寸较大的图像，长边768像素以上；

  2. 可以搭配我公开的其他lora模型，但因为训练集部分的重合需要根据情况降低权重，一般不超过0.3，其他主题的lora则需要根据实际情况调整

  3. 另外建议使用negative embedding 比如： 16-token-negative-deliberate-neg，realisticvision-negative-embedding

  4. 实质上本模型是RealisticUrbanMix没有查分之前的版本，所以可以使用其他底模搭配RealisticUrbanMix获得相似的效果，或者直接搭配RealisticUrbanMix以达到调整风格强度的效果

The city-related full-element model is trained on a large number of high-resolution renderings, and is composed of multiple models at the same time. It has strong generalization ability and is suitable for most generation scenarios related to architecture and urban design. For special scenes, it will perform better with dedicated lora and prompt words.

Recommendations:

  1. It is recommended to generate an image with a larger size, with a long side of 768 pixels or more;

  2. It can be used with other lora models that I disclosed, but because of the overlap of the training set part, the weight needs to be reduced according to the situation, generally no more than 0.3, and the lora of other topics needs to be adjusted according to the actual situation In addition,

  3. It is recommended to use negative embedding such as: 16-token-negative-deliberate-neg, realisticvision-negative-embedding

  4. In essence, this model is the version before RealisticUrbanMix did not check the score, so you can use other base models with RealisticUrbanMix to achieve similar effects, or directly match with RealisticUrbanMix to achieve the effect of adjusting the style intensity

items.name: 【Character】Medusa (Battle Through the Heavens) / 美杜莎 (斗破苍穹)
items.description:
2023/7/18 update

Upload the realistic version to generate images using arbitrary realistic models. Please make sure to set the clip skip as 2 when generating images. The generalization ability of the realistic version has been tested on multiple realistic models. See the preview images for details.

2023/7/6 update

Update dataset. Retrain the model using new craft. Adjust trigger tag to cai lin. New version is LoRA model.

Introduction

A Lycoris model trained with ~20 images of Medusa from Battle Through the Heavens. The trigger tag is ‘c-medusa’. The 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) are recommended. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version (original) YesMix. This model is a bit overfitted due to few training images, which will be fixed when dataset is updated.

Cautions (Must Read)

  • Some preview images are generated using hires fix. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

  • The maximum of generating resolution should not exceed 1024 theoretically, otherwise extra/deformed head/limbs will be waiting for you :). Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

items.name: Energetic Poses
items.description:
This is a new set of poses to the collection. This set contains a total of 46 unique dual poses, Each pose has been captured from 25 different angles, giving you a wide range of options.

Please keep in mind that due to the more dynamic poses, some images may need to be resized to fit your specific needs.

All the images in the set are in png format with the background removed, making it possible to use multiple images in a single scene without worrying about overlapping backgrounds. Additionally, the Controlnet system does not require a background to use the images, so they can be imported as they are.

However, some poses may be too far from the scene and require zooming in for stable diffusion to capture them properly.

Some poses in the set, such as those with extreme angles like top-down or bottom-right upward views, may be challenging for stable diffusion to comprehend without additional prompts support. If stable diffusion is unable to understand or generate these extreme poses, it is advisable to move on and try other poses.

items.name: ADS Girls' Frontline
items.description:
手机游戏《少女前线》中的角色“ADS”。

训练的是游戏中的默认立绘，换装立绘“水色青春”的模型已经有人在站内发布，因而此模型中没有训练。

此模型仍有许多缺陷，比如：姿势不好调整、眼睛上方的纹路生成效果不好、ADS的机械腿生成出错以及过多的腿、ADS的枪不生成或者生成出错……也许我并不能解决这些问题，凑合着用吧。

使用底模为anythingV5Anything_anythingV5Prt， 站内搜索anything v5就有。采样方法建议使用Euler a，步数在35左右效果比较好。

权重0.7左右细节较为清楚，并且稍微提高CFG Scale以调整姿势等。降低权重会丢失角色特征，但是或许会让图片质量更好，具体效果建议自己尝试。

使用高清修复可以让眼睛、手、脚等细节效果更好。放大算法建议使用ESRGAN_4x， 采样次数10，重绘幅度0.3。

由于训练的问题，模型权重较低时容易把镜头怼脸上，负面词里可加 close-up 减少这一现象。同时负面词可以加上 umbrella，因为角色头上可能会莫名其妙生成伞一样的东西。ADS的机械腿可能会被识别成丝袜，因此负面词可以加上 thighhighs。

想要贴近原版立绘的眼睛就加上 (ADS_Eyes:1.2), (symbol-shaped pupils), (symbol above eyebrows), (blue eyes), (blue thick eyebrows)

想要贴近原版立绘的很有特色的衣服就加上 ADS_OringinalSuit, transparent blue dress, puffy short sleeves

想要贴近原版立绘的手套就加上 (white gloves:1.2), perfect hands

想要ADS酷炫的机械腿就加上 ADS_MachineLeg, 你可以试着同时加上 barefoot 并且用自然语言具体描述，但是效果很可能不尽人意。

用 ADS_Hairband 生成她很有特点的发带，也许不一定要加。

用 ADS_Gun, holding gun 生成ADS的枪，不用期待效果多好。

用 squatting 和 blush 可以得到比较可爱的ADS。

其他的就祝你好运了！

Translated by Google:

The character "ADS" in the mobile game "Girls Frontline".

The training is the default costume in the game, and the model of changing costume "Aqua Youth" has been released on the site, so there is no training in this model.

This model still has many flaws, such as: poor posture adjustment, poor generation of lines above the eyes, ADS mechanical legs generated incorrectly and too many legs, ADS guns are not generated or generated incorrectly... Maybe I can't solve it Let's make do with these questions.

The base model used is anythingV5Anything_anythingV5Prt, search for anything v5 on the site. Sampling method Euler a is recommended, and the effect is better when the steps is about 35.

The details of the weight around 0.7 are clearer, and the CFG Scale is slightly increased to adjust the pose and so on. Reducing the weight will lose the characteristics of the character, but it may make the picture quality better. It is recommended to try it yourself for the specific effect.

Use high-definition repair to make eyes, hands, feet and other details better. Hires.fix is recommended to use ESRGAN_4x , steps:10, Denoising:0.3.

Due to training problems, when the weight of the model is low, it is easy to hit the camera on the face. You can add close-up to negative words to reduce this phenomenon. At the same time, negative words can be added with umbrella, because something like an umbrella may be inexplicably formed on the character's head. The mechanical legs of ADS may be recognized as stockings, so negative words can be added thighhighs.

Add (ADS_Eyes:1.2), (symbol-shaped pupils), (symbol above eyebrows), (blue eyes), (blue thick eyebrows) if you want to get close to the eyes of the original vertical painting

Add ADS_OringinalSuit, transparent blue dress, puffy short sleeves if you want to have distinctive clothes close to the original costume

Add (white gloves:1.2), perfect hands if you want to be close to the original vertical painting gloves

Add ADS_MachineLeg if you want the cool mechanical legs of ADS, you can try to add barefoot at the same time and describe it in natural language, but the effect may not be satisfactory.

Use ADS_Hairband to generate her very characteristic hairband, maybe it doesn't have to be added.

Use ADS_Gun, holding gun to generate ADS guns, don't expect good results.

You can get cute ADS with squatting and blush.

Good luck with the rest!

items.name: Yuki-Onna, the Ice Mayakashi - Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Monster
items.description:
LoRA for Yuki-Onna the Ice Mayakashi, Yuki-Onna the Icicle Mayakashi, and Yuki-Onna the Absolute Zero Mayakashi

I trained it with 128 pics, which was mainly fan art and some official art. I trained it at 20 epochs with a dim/alpha of 32/16 and with 2 steps.

Please play around with the LoRA weights. Let me know how it goes for you. Read stuff below on guidelines and known issues :)

Triggers:

  • Form 1 (ie: Ice Mayakashi) : input "YukiOnnaYGO, IceMayakashi, 1girl, pale skin" after the LoRA near the start of the prompt. Consider adding "bare thighs" or "bare legs".

  • Form 2 (ie: Icicle Mayakashi) : input "YukiOnnaYGO, IcicleMayakashi, 1girl, pale skin, white bow, sandals, medium breasts" after the LoRA near the start of the prompt. Consider adding "large breasts" or "black pantyhose".

  • Form 3 (ie: Absolute Zero Mayakashi) : input "YukiOnnaYGO, AbsoluteZeroMayakashi, 1girl, pale skin, sandals, medium breasts" after the LoRA near the start of the prompt. Consider adding "large breasts", "black pantyhose", "holding staff" and "hair ornament".

NB: can place in negative prompts if the clothes are stubbornly appearing.

Notes:

  • My experience has shown scale 0.8 ~ 1.1 works best; my best results were 1.

  • My prompt order shown in the sample pictures worked best for me.

  • Works on different models though weights may need to change for good results.

  • I used Anything4.5 model, Ambientmix, anyLora, and Midnight Maple model.

  • Refer to my pictures for examples and what upscaler I used, keep in mind I have used other textual inversions to help with poses and negatives.

LoRA trained on Malon. Apparently, no one likes her enough, so I made my own. >.<

Using "purple skirt" and "apron" probably gets closest to her (old) outfit.

Weight around 0.9~1. Maybe lower for outfit flexibility.

Maybe I'll search through the training dataset for fence images sometime... but, for now, enjoy the fences. :P

items.name: Saiki Kusuo (Saiki Kusuo no Psi-nan)

Trained on the animefull-final model for 8 epochs at a network dim of 32, then resized to one of 16. I used both screenshots from the Saiki Kusuo no Ψ Nan anime and fanart in the training dataset. Along with a few extra images from miscellaneous sources such as the manga, game and live action adaptation.

This model was trained on both the male and female version. You can just swap between them by changing 1boy to 1girl, just use Saiki Kusuo in the prompt for both of them. The outfits I explicitly tagged are their school uniforms: gakuran, summer uniform and serafuku. It's not always 100% accurate to the original uniform though, but it helps to emphasize the tag sometimes.

Include "antennas" for the limiters on his head, leaving out "glasses" sometimes works as well but it can be finnicky.
